en there's the generalized pruritus, which is itching all over the body.","dimension":9,"group":5,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.069883,0.12736,0.10744,0.09781,0.083195,0.079428,0.079318,0.075227,0.072731,0.071398,0.072249,0.063956],"unified_progress":[0.07766,0.10769,0.095739,0.090344,0.088176,0.087773,0.085222,0.087953,0.080206,0.075213,0.067579,0.05644]},{"section":11,"text":"That's a bit concerning because it's not localized.","dimension":5,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.06582,0.093836,0.097093,0.095203,0.090917,0.088858,0.088369,0.085361,0.08264,0.07983,0.073654,0.05842],"unified_progress":[0.065284,0.086808,0.08867,0.091278,0.09292,0.093824,0.091266,0.09346,0.08635,0.084831,0.071767,0.053544]},{"section":12,"text":"Pruritus can be a symptom of various conditions, including fungal infections, skin diseases, or even systemic issues like chronic kidney disease or certain blood disorders.","dimension":3,"group":6,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.036757,0.065226,0.086494,0.099692,0.099586,0.10015,0.10048,0.098914,0.093128,0.090666,0.072245,0.056658],"unified_progress":[0.037544,0.069994,0.090508,0.10061,0.10128,0.10196,0.10182,0.099127,0.093086,0.087318,0.069855,0.046911]},{"section":13,"text":"Putting this together, the combination of cervical lymphadenopathy, night sweats, and pruritus makes me think of a systemic condition.","dimension":4,"group":0,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.046939,0.078477,0.075815,0.07804,0.073293,0.073491,0.077344,0.079281,0.082964,0.093196,0.10573,0.13543],"unified_progress":[0.046528,0.068097,0.069778,0.075877,0.076501,0.083253,0.083145,0.087951,0.08983,0.091852,0.10468,0.12251]},{"section":14,"text":"One that comes to mind is chronic lymphocytic leukemia (CLL).","dimension":3,"group":6,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.032669,0.061479,0.077111,0.089195,0.090085,0.091946,0.096264,0.096142,0.095217,0.099031,0.088357,0.082504],"unified_progress":[0.033024,0.06339,0.080035,0.090304,0.092587,0.095713,0.097891,0.098302,0.096817,0.094817,0.08515,0.071969]},{"section":15,"text":"CLL is a type of blood cancer that affects the blood and lymph nodes.","dimension":2,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.024757,0.047139,0.065733,0.078383,0.09541,0.10473,0.10954,0.11381,0.11193,0.098306,0.079891,0.070366],"unified_progress":[0.029347,0.057653,0.07988,0.092381,0.099488,0.11004,0.10815,0.10491,0.098561,0.090984,0.073009,0.055594]},{"section":16,"text":"It can cause enlargement of the lymph nodes, and it's known to present with night sweats and itching as well.","dimension":2,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.031144,0.049625,0.063685,0.07591,0.092153,0.10222,0.10851,0.11467,0.11246,0.097487,0.080862,0.071278],"unified_progress":[0.035276,0.059443,0.078743,0.092959,0.098533,0.10778,0.10698,0.1045,0.097497,0.090774,0.071807,0.055711]},{"section":17,"text":"Also, CLL is something that can affect young adults, which fits this patient's age.","dimension":0,"group":5,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.039625,0.062608,0.072926,0.078657,0.084652,0.090185,0.095593,0.099223,0.10068,0.10038,0.092037,0.083433],"unified_progress":[0.04785,0.070108,0.07789,0.084638,0.089692,0.094539,0.094024,0.097681,0.093899,0.094222,0.083168,0.072288]},{"section":18,"text":"Another possibility could be something like an infection, maybe a viral one, but the night sweats and pruritus are more systemic and not typically seen in viral infections unless it's something like HIV-associated.","dimension":8,"group":6,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.03167,0.050357,0.067657,0.077118,0.086407,0.094185,0.09989,0.10735,0.11061,0.10946,0.095937,0.06937],"unified_progress":[0.038655,0.063911,0.079627,0.08927,0.094552,0.096398,0.099475,0.10131,0.098195,0.097528,0.081718,0.059365]},{"section":19,"text":"But the question is, does she have any other symptoms that point towards HIV?","dimension":5,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.0315,