an men, which fits our patient.","dimension":1,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.027473,0.042074,0.053403,0.064248,0.075428,0.087997,0.10077,0.1118,0.12312,0.12867,0.1128,0.072213],"unified_progress":[0.03661,0.056674,0.07118,0.080292,0.090245,0.096058,0.098831,0.10186,0.10121,0.10359,0.091532,0.071917]},{"section":11,"text":"But let's not jump to conclusions too quickly.","dimension":-1,"group":-1,"is_degenerate":true,"model_progress":[0.1039,0.083258,0.078498,0.071403,0.074024,0.077851,0.082865,0.093938,0.087569,0.061152,0.061636,0.12391],"unified_progress":[0.19611,0.074935,0.062973,0.063941,0.073714,0.075184,0.0929,0.086153,0.083512,0.068193,0.061848,0.060539]},{"section":12,"text":"Generalized itching could mean a few things.","dimension":4,"group":6,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.030237,0.058542,0.077762,0.092006,0.097593,0.10181,0.10605,0.1054,0.10452,0.10201,0.079431,0.044645],"unified_progress":[0.039773,0.072047,0.067911,0.095202,0.10375,0.1002,0.10237,0.1022,0.097665,0.090281,0.076371,0.052241]},{"section":13,"text":"It might be related to allergies or skin issues, but with the other symptoms, I'm thinking it's more systemic.","dimension":4,"group":6,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.018778,0.048239,0.06944,0.08599,0.09583,0.10466,0.11068,0.1136,0.11234,0.10892,0.086217,0.045311],"unified_progress":[0.0294,0.062406,0.07997,0.091244,0.097882,0.098932,0.10269,0.10379,0.10033,0.099163,0.080489,0.0537]},{"section":14,"text":"Infections like TB can cause itching due to immune responses, so that fits.","dimension":7,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.018766,0.040029,0.056083,0.070883,0.083821,0.096893,0.10878,0.11558,0.12179,0.1255,0.10313,0.05875],"unified_progress":[0.029418,0.056343,0.074809,0.086151,0.095077,0.10182,0.10331,0.10491,0.10207,0.099902,0.084775,0.061405]},{"section":15,"text":"So, putting all this together, we have painless lymph nodes, night sweats, and itching.","dimension":8,"group":9,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.018364,0.036436,0.04942,0.060142,0.06972,0.079107,0.089142,0.097423,0.10918,0.12788,0.14558,0.11761],"unified_progress":[0.030591,0.051212,0.063823,0.075186,0.083521,0.094618,0.096446,0.09997,0.10326,0.10562,0.10383,0.091918]},{"section":16,"text":"These really point towards something like tuberculosis.","dimension":4,"group":6,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.018281,0.045313,0.059048,0.070374,0.077706,0.084495,0.090212,0.091736,0.097466,0.10699,0.12791,0.13047],"unified_progress":[0.024346,0.049697,0.064439,0.074537,0.080801,0.088129,0.092606,0.097656,0.10157,0.10225,0.10928,0.11468]},{"section":17,"text":"It's a classic triad for TB, especially when you're considering the age and gender of the patient.","dimension":8,"group":9,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.02285,0.035795,0.04494,0.053438,0.061778,0.070575,0.08028,0.087904,0.1008,0.12187,0.15673,0.16304],"unified_progress":[0.028618,0.042801,0.054511,0.063874,0.072538,0.084372,0.087592,0.096302,0.10377,0.11015,0.12206,0.13341]},{"section":18,"text":"Yeah, I feel confident saying that this is probably tuberculosis.","dimension":3,"group":0,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.012885,0.024613,0.030648,0.03694,0.042261,0.048118,0.054517,0.05947,0.071696,0.099878,0.20625,0.31272],"unified_progress":[0.010698,0.021307,0.028695,0.037066,0.043303,0.059622,0.064436,0.085303,0.10236,0.11644,0.17216,0.25861]},{"section":19,"text":"The symptoms match up well, and it's a common enough condition in someone her age.","dimension":3,"group":0,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.017414,0.024473,0.030032,0.03607,0.042481,0.050226,0.059782,0.068808,0.085487,0.11773,0.19997,0.26753],"unified_progress":[0.017325,0.024701,0.031827,0.039485,0.047602,0.060686,0.066943,0.085596,0.10243,0.1205,0.16432,0.23858]},{"section":20,"text":"So, yeah, I'd go with tuberculosis as the most likely diagnosis.","dimension":3,"group":0,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.010735,0